The senior pastor of Dunamis international Gospel centre, Dr. Pst Paul Enenche in  a Crossover and New year services held on December 31, 2019 to January 1st, 2020 , at the Glory Dome Lugbe , Airport Road, Abuja  has wishes Nigerians a very happy New year . The senior pastor in a Crossover without carryover message to the church anchoring on proverbs 4:18 and psalm 84: 7, has declared for a dramatic, drastic and dimensional shift in level. According to the pastor, the part of the just is a shining light that shines more and more until the perfect day,’ they go from strength to strength everyone of them in Zion appearing before God. He emphasized that though we have prayed, prayed and we are still praying, but despite the  weakness in our spirits, God has heard our prayers and we are to expect a shift in level, dimensionally in this year 2020. “We are to expect a spiritual explosion, especially as we made ourselves available and ready to Know God, we are to expect God to move in unusual way over our land such that things would change,’ he prayed. Reflecting on her husband’s message, Dr. Pst Becky Enenche echoes that all the declarations by the senior pastor, Enenche, having heard directly from God, prayed that  time has come for a shift in level, dramatic, drastic and dimensional shift in level as individuals and as a nation. Therefore, wishes Nigerians a very happy new year, better things, greater things and more blessings in year 2020. 